@startuml
!theme plain
title ProspectOS - B2B Prospecting System Use Cases

left to right direction

' Actors
actor "Sales Rep" as sales
actor "Sales Manager" as manager
actor "Marketing Team" as marketing
actor "System Admin" as admin

' External systems as actors (recommended in use case diagrams)
actor "Python Scraper" as scraper <<system>>
actor "LLM Provider" as llm <<system>>

rectangle "ProspectOS System" {
  ' Core prospecting use cases
  usecase "Add Company Manually" as UC1
  usecase "Import Company List" as UC2
  usecase "Enrich Company Data" as UC3
  usecase "Score Company" as UC4
  usecase "Qualify Prospect" as UC5

  ' ICP Management
  usecase "Create ICP Profile" as UC6
  usecase "Update ICP Criteria" as UC7
  usecase "Match Company to ICP" as UC8

  ' AI-Powered Analysis
  usecase "Auto-Scrape Website" as UC9
  usecase "Analyze Company Signals" as UC10
  usecase "Generate Outreach Strategy" as UC11
  usecase "Monitor Company News" as UC12

  ' Workflow Management
  usecase "Review Prospects Queue" as UC13
  usecase "Update Prospect Status" as UC14
  usecase "Generate Reports" as UC15

  ' System Administration
  usecase "Configure AI Providers" as UC16
  usecase "Monitor System Health" as UC17
  usecase "Manage User Access" as UC18
}

' Relationships (primary actors)
sales --> UC1
sales --> UC3
sales --> UC5
sales --> UC13
sales --> UC14

manager --> UC2
manager --> UC6
manager --> UC7
manager --> UC15

marketing --> UC8
marketing --> UC11
marketing --> UC12

admin --> UC16
admin --> UC17
admin --> UC18

' External systems interactions (as supporting actors)
scraper --> UC3
scraper --> UC9
scraper --> UC12

llm --> UC4
llm --> UC8
llm --> UC10
llm --> UC11

' Dependencies / includes (more UML-ish than "requires")
UC4 .> UC3 : <<include>>
UC5 .> UC4 : <<include>>
UC8 .> UC6 : <<include>>
UC11 .> UC10 : <<include>>
UC13 .> UC4 : <<include>>

note right of scraper
Python application that:
- Scrapes company websites
- Searches news/signals
- Extracts contact info
- Identifies tech stack
end note

note right of llm
AI providers (OpenAI, Anthropic)
for intelligent analysis:
- Company scoring
- ICP matching
- Strategy generation
end note

@enduml
